PN,43601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781168735
OL,3,CWoman who strangled elderly mother at
OL,4,CChristmas jailed for eight years
OL,6,FA daughter who strangled her elderly
OL,7,Fmother with a belt on Christmas
OL,8,Fmorning before attempting to take her
OL,9,Fown life has been jailed for eight
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FStefania Glowka, 64, killed Tamara
OL,13,FGlowka, 86, at their home in Devizes,
OL,14,FWiltshire, on 25 December last year.
OL,16,FGlowka pleaded guilty to manslaughter
OL,17,Fby reason of diminished responsibility
OL,18,Fand was acquitted of murder by a
OL,19,Funanimous jury following a trial at
OL,20,FBristol Crown Court.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781168735
OL,3,CWoman who strangled elderly mother at
OL,4,CChristmas jailed for eight years
OL,6,FJudge Julian Lambert told Glowka that
OL,7,Fdetermining the correct sentence in
OL,8,Fthe case was "difficult", with Glowka
OL,9,Fstating that she wished to serve her
OL,10,Fsentence and then take her own life
OL,11,Ffollowing her release.
OL,13,FThe judge said: "This is an utterly
OL,14,Fextraordinary and deeply sad case.
OL,15,FYour mother had no one else in the
OL,16,Fworld but you. You had no one else in
OL,17,Fthe world but your mother.
OL,19,F"You were devoted to one another and
OL,20,Fyou loved your mother as deeply as she
OL,21,Floved you.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@XO]uD@QOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781168735
OL,3,CWoman who strangled elderly mother at
OL,4,CChristmas jailed for eight years
OL,6,F"You showed extraordinary kindness to
OL,7,Fyour mother and you gave her the
OL,8,Fhighest level of care."
OL,10,FThe court heard Glowka had been the
OL,11,Fprimary carer for her mother, who she
OL,12,Flived and shared a bedroom with, and
OL,13,Fher mother had recently been diagnosed
OL,14,Fwith schizophrenia.
OL,16,FJurors were told Glowka, who never
OL,17,Fmarried or had children of her own,
OL,18,Fsaid she wanted to "let mum go" after
OL,19,Fboth women experienced a deterioration
OL,20,Fin their mental health.
OL,26,@pD@WO]zD@TOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781168735
OL,3,CWoman who strangled elderly mother at
OL,4,CChristmas jailed for eight years
OL,6,FGlowka prepared her mother's favourite
OL,7,Fmeal on Christmas Eve, with the women
OL,8,Fspending the evening together before
OL,9,Fgoing to bed.
OL,11,FOvernight, Glowka struggled to sleep
OL,12,Fand felt she had no energy to continue
OL,13,Fto care for her mother.
OL,15,FShe later told police it was a "spur
OL,16,Fof the moment" decision to strangle
OL,17,Fher using a belt as she rose from her
OL,18,Fbed to use the bathroom in the early
OL,19,Fhours of the morning.
OL,26,@wD@`OUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781168735
OL,3,CWoman who strangled elderly mother at
OL,4,CChristmas jailed for eight years
OL,6,FGlowka then laid next to her deceased
OL,7,Fmother and attempted to take her own
OL,8,Flife, in what the judge described as
OL,9,F"the most determined effort".
OL,11,F"You did not succeed in your attempted
OL,12,Fsuicide and when you awoke either from
OL,13,Fsleep or unconsciousness you rang the
OL,14,Fpolice and told them what you had
OL,15,Fdone," he told her.
OL,17,F"You admitted responsibility at the
OL,18,Fscene and when interviewed by the
OL,19,Fpolice."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@\O]sD@AOUwD@FO]yD@AOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781168735
OL,3,CWoman who strangled elderly mother at
OL,4,CChristmas jailed for eight years
OL,6,FWhen officers arrived at the property,
OL,7,FGlowka directed them to a box
OL,8,Fcontaining documents including a
OL,9,Fletter addressed to a close friend.
OL,11,FThis stated: "I killed my mum as I
OL,12,Fcannot continue to look after her and
OL,13,FI love her too much to put her into an
OL,14,Finstitutionalised care."
OL,16,FTwo psychiatrists assessed Glowka and
OL,17,Fbelieved she was suffering from a
OL,18,Frecurrent depressive disorder, the
OL,19,Fcourt heard.
OL,26,@sD@NOUvD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781168735
OL,3,CWoman who strangled elderly mother at
OL,4,CChristmas jailed for eight years
OL,6,FAll 12 members of the jury returned
OL,7,Ffollowing their verdict to watch Judge
OL,8,FLambert sentence Glowka on Tuesday
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,11,FOne female juror wept as Nicholas
OL,12,FCorsellis KC read a letter from
OL,13,FGlowka, which she had written to the
OL,14,Fjudge ahead of the verdict.
OL,16,FIn the letter, Glowka described her
OL,17,Fmother as "the best mother in the
OL,18,Fwhole world" and always made her feel
OL,19,F"much loved and cherished".
OL,26,@yD@KOUzD@LO]{D@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781168735
OL,3,CWoman who strangled elderly mother at
OL,4,CChristmas jailed for eight years
OL,6,F"I learnt from her how to tell right
OL,7,Ffrom wrong and I feel very bad that I
OL,8,Flet her down at her most vulnerable,
OL,9,Fwhen she needed me the most," she
OL,10,Fwrote.
OL,12,F"My crime violated so many written and
OL,13,Funwritten codes."
OL,15,FGlowka said she felt bad for
OL,16,F"betraying the oath" she took 10 years
OL,17,Fago when she became a UK citizen and
OL,18,Ffelt "very ashamed" of herself.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@]O]tD@AOUuD@QO]xD@AOUxD@TO]zD@
OL,26,AFOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781168735
OL,3,CWoman who strangled elderly mother at
OL,4,CChristmas jailed for eight years
OL,6,F"The only way I can repay my debt to
OL,7,Fthe country that took me in is by
OL,8,Fworking in prison to improve the
OL,9,Fenvironment for other prisoners and
OL,10,Fstaff, because they also matter," she
OL,11,Fcontinued.
OL,13,F"I know mother would have wanted that,
OL,14,Fbecause she always worked so hard and
OL,15,Fwas the best example I had in front of
OL,16,Fmy eyes, all my life.
OL,18,F"I made myself a pariah, outside
OL,19,Fcivilised society, and I feel I don't
OL,20,Fhave the right to return or belong
OL,21,Fthere anymore.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@aO]uD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781168735
OL,3,CWoman who strangled elderly mother at
OL,4,CChristmas jailed for eight years
OL,6,F"My mother is with me everyday. I talk
OL,7,Fto her and often hear her voice. I had
OL,8,Fa shining light in my life and I
OL,9,Fextinguished it. Now there is only
OL,10,Fdarkness around me."
OL,12,FSpeaking after the case, detective
OL,13,Fsergeant Chris Hughes of Wiltshire
OL,14,FPolice described the incident as
OL,15,F"incredibly sad".
OL,17,F"I'd like to thank and pay tribute to
OL,18,Fall the officers who attended this
OL,19,Fincident, as well as the various staff
OL,20,Ffrom our partner agencies," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@TO]wD@AOUwD@PO]yD@AOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781168735
OL,3,CWoman who strangled elderly mother at
OL,4,CChristmas jailed for eight years
OL,6,F"It can't have been easy on a day
OL,7,Fwhich revolves around family, but they
OL,8,Fdealt with this incident with the
OL,9,Fusual professionalism, care and
OL,10,Fdiligence."
